Feature: Connect with people through facebook

Scenario: Create new account in facebook

Given user can launch the facebook url

When user can click the create my account button

And user can enters the first name and last name in the given field

And user can enters either mobile or email address

And user can set the password for security purpose

And user can choose their date of birth

And user can select their gender

And user can click the sign up button

Then user can succussfully create the account in facebook
